<COREF ID="4" TYPE="IDENT">The main <COREF ID="5" TYPE="IDENT">UN</COREF> forum on human rights</COREF> is accusing <COREF ID="0" TYPE="IDENT">Israel</COREF> of war crimes and human rights abuses in <COREF ID="10" TYPE="IDENT">the Palestinian territories</COREF> .
