<COREF ID="2" TYPE="IDENT">The <COREF ID="5" TYPE="IDENT">UN</COREF> resolution</COREF> also calls for the setting up of what <COREF ID="2" TYPE="IDENT">it</COREF> calls <COREF ID="1" TYPE="IDENT">the Human Rights Enquiry Commission</COREF> .
